<p>You must not use, reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works based on any personal creations of Visiuun, including but not limited to characters, products, artworks, designs, or any intellectual property without express written consent from Visiuun. This includes but is not limited to the use of Visiuun's creations on social media, websites, or any commercial or non-commercial platforms.</p>

