<h3>5. Personal Disputes and Issues</h3>
<p>Any personal disputes or issues must be resolved privately and directly with Visiuun. Should you engage in harassment, threats, or disruptive behavior in personal communication, Visiuun reserves the right to block, report, or sever contact with you permanently.</p>

<h3>6. No Third-Party Involvement</h3>
<p>Any matter involving Visiuun should not be escalated to third parties or external parties without prior mutual consent. Disputes will be handled directly between the parties involved, and Visiuun is under no obligation to involve others in personal matters.</p>

<h3>7. Confidentiality</h3>
<p>Any personal or sensitive information shared during communication is considered confidential. Visiuun will respect privacy but is not responsible for any information you choose to share. Unauthorized distribution or misuse of any private information is prohibited and will lead to immediate cessation of contact.</p>

<h3>8. No Assumption of Liability</h3>
<p>Visiuun is not liable for any personal misunderstandings, miscommunications, or issues arising from interactions. All engagements are voluntary and based on mutual consent. If disagreements or issues arise, they should be addressed directly and respectfully, within the confines of personal communication.</p>

<h3>9. Final Authority on Communication</h3>
