<h3>10. Dispute Resolution and Legal Action</h3>
<p>Any legal disputes, including but not limited to violations of intellectual property rights or personal communication, will be resolved through direct negotiation between the involved parties. If an amicable resolution cannot be reached, Visiuun reserves the right to pursue legal action through appropriate channels. This may include filing complaints or lawsuits as necessary to protect personal creations and rights.</p>

